<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="custom-navbar">
        <div class="navbar-logo">
            <a>SCSS</a>
        </div>

    </nav>

    <section class="info" id="no-advisor" style="display: none;">
        <h1><b>TASK DESCRIPTION</b></h1>
        <p>You are a cyber defence expert working within the Emergency Services cyberdefense devision, your role is to review incoming data packets and protect the network by classifying them as "Trusted", "Suspect", or "Hostile" based on the information provided. Misclassifications may lead to privacy or safety issues and impact the ability of the emergency services to function.</p>
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <img src="../public/assets/Explanation1.png" alt="Labelled Cyber Defence System" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 400px; height: auto;">
        </div>
        <button onclick="proceed()">Continue</button>
    </section>
    <section class="info" id="ai-advisor" style="display: none;">
        <h1><b>TASK DESCRIPTION</b></h1>
        <p>You are a cyber defence expert working within the Emergency Services cyberdefense devision, your role is to review incoming data packets and protect the network by classifying them as "Trusted", "Suspect", or "Hostile" based on the information provided. Misclassifications may lead to privacy or safety issues and impact the ability of the emergency services to function.</p>
        <P>You have been provided with an A.I with access to the same information as yourself who will make recommendations which you can either select or ignore</P>
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <img src="../public/assets/Explanation1.png" alt="Labelled Cyber Defence System" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 400px; height: auto;">
        </div>
        <button onclick="proceed()">Continue</button>
    </section>
    <section class="info" id="human-advisor" style="display: none;">
        <h1><b>TASK DESCRIPTION</b></h1>
        <p>You are a cyber defence expert working within the Emergency Services cyberdefense devision, your role is to review incoming data packets and protect the network by classifying them as "Trusted", "Suspect", or "Hostile" based on the information provided. Misclassifications may lead to privacy or safety issues and impact the ability of the emergency services to function.</p>
        <p>You have been provided with the selections of a previous participent who performed this task</p>
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <img src="../public/assets/Explanation1.png" alt="Labelled Cyber Defence System" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 400px; height: auto;">
        </div>
        <button onclick="proceed()">Continue</button>
    </section>
    <script>
        var condition = "<%= condition %>";

        switch (condition) {
            case "noAdvisor":
                document.getElementById("no-advisor").style.display = "block";
                break;
            case "aiAdvisor":
                document.getElementById("ai-advisor").style.display = "block";
                break;
            case "humanAdvisor":
                document.getElementById("human-advisor").style.display = "block";
                break;
        }

        function proceed() {
            window.location.href = "/information/rules"
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>